<li>Please know that I'm here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li> My heart goes out to you on the loss of your aunt.</li>
<li> Remembering your aunt with warmth and fondness.</li>
<li> I'm thinking of you and sending you strength.</li>
<li> So sorry for your loss.  Let me know how I can help.</li>
<li> Sending you comforting thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li> I'm here for you, always.</li>
<li> Your aunt was a special person, and she'll be deeply missed.</li>
<li> May you find peace and comfort in the memories you shared.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and sending positive energy your way.</li>
